# 🛒 Superstore Sales Analysis with SQL + Python + AI Integration

This project explores sales performance using SQL and Python on a retail dataset. It uses **Databricks SQL** for deep business analysis and **OpenAI GPT-4** for summarizing insights into actionable recommendations.

---

## 📌 Project Highlights

- 📊 Performed advanced sales and profit analysis with SQL
- 🧹 Cleaned messy data and converted currency columns into usable formats
- 📈 Visualized key insights using Matplotlib
- 🤖 Used GPT-4 to generate business summaries and improvement suggestions

